name: "ocp-browser"
version: "1.1.7"
synopsis:
  "Console browser for the documentation of installed OCaml libraries"
description: """
ocp-browser is a ncurses-like interface that allows to easily browse the
interfaces and documentation of all installed OCaml modules."""
